## 3ï¸âƒ£ TOTP (Authenticator Apps) â­â­â­â­

**How it works**

* Time-based codes every 30s
* Apps: Google Authenticator, Authy, Microsoft Authenticator

**Standards**

* RFC 6238 (industry standard)

**Used by**

* Google
* GitHub
* AWS
* Stripe

**Pros**

* Offline
* Secure
* No SMS
* Widely trusted

**Cons**

* User can lose phone
* Needs backup codes

**Verdict**
âœ… **BEST default choice**

